    var isMobile = window.matchMedia("only screen and (max-width: 39.9375em)");

    $(function() {
        $(document).scroll(function() {
            var y = $(this).scrollTop();
            var el = $('.row-emg-top__tb-filters');
            var form = $('.emg-top__form');
            var mobileExtra = 0;
            if (isMobile.matches) {
                mobileExtra = 450;
            }
        });
        var filter = $('#emg-filter-extra-slide-container');
        var button = $('.emg-top__form-filter-all-button');
        var buttonText = $('#emg-filter-extra-slide');
        var buttonIcon = button.find('i');
        button.click(function() {
            filter.slideToggle(100,
                function() {
                    if ($(filter).is(':visible')) {
                        buttonIcon.addClass('fa-rotate-180');
                        buttonText.text('Hide filters');
                        $('.search-header-filter-container').hide();
                        $('.search-header-form-filter').removeClass('sf-filter-open');
                    } else {
                        buttonIcon.removeClass('fa-rotate-180');
                        buttonText.text('Show all filters');
                    }
                });
        });

        var heightDektop = 110;
        var heightMobile = 120;
    });
</script>

<script>
    let heightDesktop = 110;
    let heightMobile = 120;

    if(isMobile.matches) {
        let topHeader = document.querySelector(".emg-top__header-style");
        if(topHeader) {
            topHeader.setAttribute("height", 55);
        }

        let topText = document.querySelector(".emg-module__text-style");
        if(topText) {
            topText.setAttribute("height", heightMobile);
        }
    } else {
        let topHeader = document.querySelector(".emg-top__header-style");
        if(topHeader) {
            topHeader.setAttribute("height", 95);
        }

        let topText = document.querySelector(".emg-module__text-style");
        if(topText) {
            topText.setAttribute("height", heightDesktop);
        }
    }
</script>

    $.ajax({
        type: 'GET',
        dataType: 'json',
        url: '/search-sponsor/sponsor',
        data: 'categoryId=4273',
        success: function (result) {
            if (result.hasSponsor) {
                var slots = $('.emg-serp__serp-container > div.emg-serp__row');
                var slotPositionToInsertSearchSponsorAfter = 6;
                if (slots.length <= 5)
                    slotPositionToInsertSearchSponsorAfter = slots.length;
                $('.emg-serp__serp-container > div.emg-serp__row').eq(slotPositionToInsertSearchSponsorAfter - 1).after('<div class="emg-serp__row emg-serp__row-recommend">'+ result.html + '<div>');
            }
        }
    });
</script>

    function addImpressionToList(id, item, index) {
        if (item.Items.id.Value.toString() === id) {
            var position = (pageSize * (page - 1)) + (index + 1);
            var impression = emg.enhancedEcommerce.getImpression(id, item, position, searchType);

            impressionIds.push(id);
            impressions.push(impression);
        }
    }

    $(document.body).on('touchmove', onScroll);
    $(window).on('scroll', onScroll);

    function onScroll(){
        $(window).scrollEnd(function () {
            emg.enhancedEcommerce.sendImpressions(impressions, priorityListings, searchType, '4273,,,,');
        }, 2000);
    }

    $.fn.scrollEnd = function (callback, timeout) {
        $(this).on('scroll', function () {
            var $this = $(this);
            if ($this.data('scrollTimeout')) {
                clearTimeout($this.data('scrollTimeout'));
            }
            $this.data('scrollTimeout', setTimeout(callback, timeout));
        });
    };

    <div id="divSearchTextBottomContainer" class="search-text-bottom" style="margin-top:20px;">
        <a name="moreAboutSearch"></a>
        <p>Data is quickly proving to be one of the most valuable resources of the 21st century, with analytics serving as the catalyst that brings it to life. Businesses and organisations across all sectors are now capable of harnessing the hidden value of the information in the masses of data collected and stored in their systems.</p>
<p></p>
<p>Thanks to cutting edge data analytics software and techniques, they are investing an increased amount of resources into discovering the valuable insights hidden in their data. Businesses and organisations can use these insights to detect emerging trends and changing behaviours, in turn increasing&nbsp;their competitive advantage, long-term sustainability and revenue.</p>
<p></p>
<h3></h3>
<h3>Meet the demand with a data analytics course</h3>
<p>In a data driven economy in which data sciences are increasingly being adopted by companies across all industries, the demand for data fluent and tech-savvy employees is far exceeding the available supply and thus companies are struggling to recruit the required talent for their business intelligence and data analytics ambitions.</p>
<p></p>
<p>Data analytics courses will equip you with the unique set of skills needed to meet this demand and begin converting data into valuable insights. There are a great range of training options available for newcomers as well as those looking to sharpen existing skills, learn to use analytics software or focus on a specific field of data analysis, such as business or fraud prevention for example.&nbsp;</p>
<h3></h3>
<h3></h3>
<h3>Who is a data analytics course suited to?</h3>
<p>Since data analytics is relevant and beneficial to professionals in a wide range of industries, governmental institutions and research organizations, course participants are likely to be made up of a variety of professional backgrounds and motivations. Here are some examples:</p>
<ul>
<li>University graduates interested in pursuing a career in data science and business analytics</li>
<li>Professionals seeking to enhance their knowledge and broaden their skillset in the fields of data science, business intelligence and data-driven decision making.</li>
<li>Entrepreneurs who aim to start a new business or grow an existing one by enhancing it with data-related components and capabilities</li>
<li>Decision-makers, leaders and managers interested in acquiring the necessary knowledge and skillset in the field of data science and business intelligence in order to be able to compete on analytics rather than on intuition alone.</li>
<li>Life-long learners interested in broadening their knowledge in the new field of data science and business analytics</li>
</ul>
<h3></h3>
<h3></h3>
<h3></h3>
<h3>Data analytics course content</h3>
<p>Most data analytics courses serve to provide a broad familiarity with the relevant concepts of data analytics and data science and how they can be applied to a wide range of business, scientific and engineering problems. Courses will survey techniques and methods, drawing on applications from social, political, economic, legal, and business and marketing fields.&nbsp;</p>
<p></p>
<p>Topics covered could include:</p>
<div class="emg-columns emg-columns-2 emg-background-flex emg-columns-50">
<div class="emg-column">
<ul>
<li>History of data analytics and data science</li>
<li>Defining key terms and understanding analytics jargon</li>
<li>The key drivers for data analytics (data, math, computation and analysis)</li>
<li>The different types of data</li>
<li>The different concepts of machine learning</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="emg-column">
<ul>
<li>Interpreting, reporting, and visualizing the results of data analytics</li>
<li>Computational and data storage considerations for data analytics</li>
<li>Big Data tools and techniques</li>
<li>Current trends in data analytics</li>
<li>Harnessing artificial intelligence&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<p></p>
<h3></h3>
<h3></h3>
<h3></h3>
<h3>Data analytics software courses</h3>
<p>Many data analytics courses will have a software-focused approach, and there are a variety of effective tools to choose from that enable users to retrieve, combine, interact with, explore, and visualise data from any combination of sources.</p>
<p></p>
<p>From <a href="/search/oracle-training-courses">Oracle </a>to <a href="/search/microsoft-excel-training-courses">Excel</a>, data analytics software provides companies and organisations with greater insight into their business processes, their market, and their customers. Fast, convenient access to enterprise information improves decision making and enhances business performance overall.</p>
    </div>

    $(function () {
        $('.serp-sorting').click(function () {
            $(this).addClass('serp-sorting-open');
            $('.serp-sorting-list').slideToggle("fast", function () {
                $(this).toggleClass('serp-sorting-list-open');
                $('.serp-sorting-icon').toggleClass('fa-caret-down').toggleClass('fa-caret-up');
            });
        });

        $(document).mouseup(function (e) {
            var container = $('.serp-sorting-list');
            var switcher = $('.serp-sorting');

            if (!container.is(e.target) && !switcher.is(e.target) && !switcher.is($(e.target).parent()) && container.has(e.target).length === 0) {
                container.hide();
                $('.serp-sorting-icon').removeClass('fa-caret-up').addClass('fa-caret-down');
            };
        });
    });

        
    $(document).ready(function () {
        if (window.location.hash.indexOf("#scroll=") == 0) {
            $(window).scrollTop(parseInt(window.location.hash.substr(8)));
        }
    });

        $(this).attr("href", $(this).attr("href") + "#scroll=" + $(window).scrollTop());
    });

<script type="text/javascript">
    var compareCookie = 'compare';
    $(function () {

        $('.icon-wishlist').click(function (e) {
            e.stopPropagation();
            e.preventDefault();
            if ($(this).hasClass('fa-heart-o')) {
                $(this).removeClass('fa-heart-o').addClass('fa-heart');
                $(this).prop('checked', true);
            } else {
                $(this).removeClass('fa-heart').addClass('fa-heart-o');
                $(this).prop('checked', false);
            }
            $(this).trigger("ifToggled");
        });

        var compareButton = $('.rcb-compare-button');
			var compareButtonExtra = compareButton.height();


				if (isDesktop.matches) {
					$(window).scroll(function() {
						var windowTop = $(window).scrollTop();
						var windowLeft = compareButton.offset().left;
						var stickyTop = compareButton.offset().top + compareButtonExtra;
						var box = $('.rcb-compare-button-sticky');
						if (stickyTop < windowTop){
							$('body').prepend(box);
							box.slideDown('fast').find('.compare-length').html('(' + $('.rcb-compare-list li').length + ')');
						}
						else
							box.slideUp('fast');
					});
				}

        

        $('.rcb-compare-button, .rcb-compare-button-sticky').click(function() {
            var els = $('.rcb-compare-list li, .rcb-compare-visited-list li');
            var ids = $.unique(els.map(function(){return $(this).data("id");}).get()).join(',');

            location = '/Education/Compare?educationIds=' + ids;
        });

        $('#list').on('ifToggled', '.searchCheckbox', function(e) {
            var cb = $(this);
            var c = cb.prop('checked');
            $('body').prepend($('.compare-alert'));
            var compareAlert = $('.compare-alert');
            var compareExist = compareAlert.length > 0;
            var cw = compareExist ? compareAlert.outerWidth() : null;


            var rc = $('.rcb-compare').parents('.RCWhite');
            if (c) {
                rc.stop().animate({ backgroundColor: '#ebf8ff' }, 300, 'swing', function() {
                    rc.delay(800).animate({ backgroundColor: '#ffffff' }, 300);
                });

                if (compareExist) {
                    compareAlert.css({
                        position: "absolute",
                        display: "block",
                        top: (cb.offset().top - 25) + "px",
                        left: (cb.offset().left - cw - 10) + "px"
                    }).fadeIn('fast', function() {
                        $(this).delay(3000).fadeOut('slow', function() {
                            compareAlert.remove();
                        });
                    });
                }

                var url = $('.search-result-col-education a', cb.parents('tr')).attr('href');
                addCompareEdu(cb.data('education-id'), cb.data('name'), cb.data('institute-name'), url);
            } else {
                removeCompareEdu(cb.data('education-id'));
            }
        });

        var cv = cookies.read(compareCookie);
        if (cv) {
            $.getJSON('/educations/compare/get-list?educationIds=' + cv, function(d) {
                if (d.status) {
                    for (var i = 0; i < d.educations.length; i++) {
                        var edu = d.educations[i];
                        var eduElm = $('.searchCheckbox.edu' + edu.Id);

                        addCompareEdu(edu.Id, edu.Name, edu.InstituteName, edu.Url, true);
                        eduElm.attr('checked', true).parent().iCheck('check');

                        if (eduElm.hasClass('fa-heart-o')) {
                            eduElm.removeClass('fa-heart-o').addClass('fa-heart');    
                        }

                    }
                }
            });
        }

        if (false) {
            var visitedEducations = (cookies.read('LatestVisitedEducations_12') || '').replace(/educationId=/ig, '').replace(/&/ig, ',');

            if (visitedEducations) {
                $.getJSON('/educations/compare/get-list?educationIds=' + visitedEducations, function(d) {
                    if (d.status) {
                        for (var i = 0; i < (d.educations.length > 3 ? 3 : d.educations.length); i++) {
                            var edu = d.educations[i];
                            addCompareEdu(edu.Id, edu.Name, edu.InstituteName, edu.Url, true, '.rcb-compare-visited-list');
                        }

                        if (d.educations.length > 0)
                            $('.rcb-compare-visited-divider').show();
                    }
                });
            }
        }

        toggleCompareTexts();
    });

    function toggleCompareTexts() {

        var totalCount = getCompareCount();
        var withoutVisited = getCompareCount(true);
        var empty = $('.rcb-compare-empty');
        var button = $('.rcb-compare-button');
        var emptyVisited = $('.rcb-compare-empty-with-visited');
        if (getCompareCount() < 2) {
            empty.show();
            button.hide();
        } else {
            empty.hide();
            button.show();
        }

        if (totalCount > 1 && withoutVisited == 0)
            emptyVisited.show();
        else 
            emptyVisited.hide();
    }

    function addCompareEdu(eid, name, instname, url, skipCookie, visitedEdu) {
        var l = $(visitedEdu ? '.rcb-compare-visited-list' : '.rcb-compare-list');
        var li = $('<li class="edu' + eid + '" data-id="' + eid + '"><a href="' + url + '" class="rcb-compare-edu">' + name + '</a><span class="rcb-compare-ins">' + instname + '</span><div class="rcb-compare-delete"><i class="fa fa-times" aria-hidden="true"></i></div></li>');
        l.append(li);
        $('.rcb-compare-delete', li).click(function () { removeCompareEdu(eid, visitedEdu); });

        toggleCompareTexts();

        if (!skipCookie)
        {
            var cv = cookies.read(compareCookie) || ',';
            if (cv.indexOf(',' + eid + ',') == -1)
                cookies.create(compareCookie, cv + eid + ',', 1);
        }

        $('.compare-length').html(getCompareCount());
    }

    function getCompareCount(excludeVisited) {
        return $('.rcb-compare-list').find('li').length + (excludeVisited ? 0 : $('.rcb-compare-visited-list').find('li').length);
    }

    function removeCompareEdu(id, visitedEdu) {
        var l = $(visitedEdu ? '.rcb-compare-visited-list' : '.rcb-compare-list');
        $('li.edu' + id, l).remove();

        var checkbox = $('.searchCheckbox.edu' + id);
        if (!visitedEdu && !checkbox.hasClass('fa-heart'))
            checkbox.attr('checked', false).parent().removeClass('ez-checked');
        else if (!visitedEdu && checkbox.hasClass('fa-heart'))
            checkbox.removeClass('fa-heart').addClass('fa-heart-o');
        
        toggleCompareTexts();

        if ($('.rcb-compare-visited-list').find('li').length == 0) {
            $('.rcb-compare-visited-divider').hide();
        }

        $('.compare-length').html(getCompareCount());

        //$('.compare-action-del').fadeIn('slow', function() { setTimeout(function() { $('.compare-action-del').fadeOut('slow') }, 1500); });

        if (!visitedEdu) {   
            var cv = cookies.read(compareCookie) || ',';
            if (cv.indexOf(',' + id + ',') > -1)
                cookies.create(compareCookie, cv.replace(',' + id + ',', ','), 1);
        }
    };
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
    function rcbNewsletterSubscribe() {
        $.post('/newsletter/rcb-subscribe?email=' + $('#txtTo').val(),
            function (obj) {
                if (obj.sent) {
                    $('#txtTo').val('');
                    $("#spSendMessage").show(); 
                }
            }
        );
    }

	$("#newsLetterForm-rcb").validate(
        {
            submitHandler: function (f) {
                rcbNewsletterSubscribe();
            },
            rules: {
                approvedConditions: {
                    required: true
                }
            },
            messages: {
                txtTo: "Email address is missing.",
                approvedConditions: {
                    required: "In order to continue please accept the Terms & Conditions and Privacy Policy"
                }
            },
            errorPlacement: function (error, element) {
                if (element.attr("name") === "approvedConditions") {
                    $("#acceptanceErrorMessage").show();
                    error.appendTo($("#acceptanceErrorMessage"));
                } else {
                    $("#spErrorMessage").show();
                    error.appendTo($("#spErrorMessage"));
                }
            },
            //success: function(element) {
            //    $("#spErrorMessage").hide();
            //},
            debug:true
            });               
</script>

<script>
    var footerHeader = $('.footer-header-sites');
    var footerMenu = $('.footer-site-menu');
    var footerToggler = $('.emg-footer__network-sites');
    var footerSites = $('.emg-sites');
    var footerSitesInner = $('.emg-sites-inner');
    var footerOpen = 'is-open';

    footerToggler.click(function () {
        $(this).find('button').toggleClass('is-open');
        $(this).find('i').toggleClass('is-open');
        footerSites.fadeToggle('fast');
    });
    footerToggler.click(function (event) { event.stopPropagation(); });

    footerHeader.click(function () {
        footerMenu.slideToggle('slow');
        $(this).find('i').toggleClass('fa-rotate-180');
    });

    $(window).click(function (e) {
        if (footerSites.is(':visible')) {
            if (!footerSitesInner.is(e.target) && footerSitesInner.has(e.target).length === 0) {
                footerSites.css('display', 'none');
                footerToggler.toggleClass('is-open');
                footerToggler.find('i').toggleClass('is-open');
            }
        }
    });

    var elements = document.getElementsByClassName("JavascriptAction");

    var myFunction = function () {
        alert('Success!');
    };

    for (var i = 0; i < elements.length; i++) {
        elements[i].addEventListener('click', myFunction, false);
    }

</script>

lists_2 = soup.find_all('div', class_="emg-serp__row emg-serp__row-has-reviews emg-serp__row-has-compare")

data =[ ]

    course_title = list_.find('a', class_="emg-serp__link").text.replace('\n',' ').split('    ')

    data.append(course_title)

data =[ ]


for list_ in lists_2:
    course_title = list_.find('a', class_="emg-serp__link").text.replace('\n\n\n',' ').split('\n')
   
       
    print(course_title)
    print()
    data.append(course_title)
    

    

info_2 = pd.DataFrame(data)

info_2.columns = ['course_title','1','course_subtitle', 'course_description','3', 'course_type', 'duration','2', 'price','4', 'location', 'course_delivery','5']
info_2['course_delivery1'] = info_2['course_delivery'].astype(str) + info_2["5"].astype(str)
info_2 = info_2.drop(['1','2','3', '4', '5', 'course_delivery'],  axis=1)
info_2.rename(columns={"course_delivery1": "course_delivery"})
print(info_2)
    

info_2.to_csv('housing1csv', index=False)
